Ranger Help for: hunt
=====================

SYNTAX:      hunt <creature>
USAGE:       Wilderness
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     60
SKILL TYPE:  hunting

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to track and attack a creature in an adjacent
room. The Ranger uses their tracking abilities to locate the target, then
automatically moves to the target's room and initiates combat. The
creature must be in a room directly adjacent to the Ranger. This skill
combines the Ranger's tracking expertise with combat readiness, allowing
them to close distance quickly and strike before the prey can react.
